headline: Are These 3 Top-Performing Tech Stocks in the Nasdaq-100, Up 33% to 64% in 2025, Still a Buy Now?
summary: The Nasdaq-100 is nearly flat year to date, but don't tell these three red-hot technology stocks.

headline: Prediction: This Will Be the First Mega Technology Company to Split Its Stock in 2025 (and It Isn't Tesla)
summary: Netflix's soaring stock price means it is likely to split its stock soon.  Stock splits garner a lot of attention from individual investors.  One technology stock that has been suspiciously absent from the stock split game is Netflix (NASDAQ: NFLX).
